Modifications made by CES GLOBAL include, but are not limited to:

  1. Full Vietnamese translation of all 31 skill definitions (SKILL.md)
     and supporting reference files (data_sources.md, gotchas.md,
     output_template.md, thresholds.md).
  2. Renaming of all 31 skill identifiers from English to Vietnamese
     (e.g., "cash-flow-snapshot" → "du-bao-dong-tien").
  3. Restructuring of plugin documentation (README.md) according to an
     enterprise organizational chart model with four functional departments:
     Operations, Finance, Marketing & Sales, Human Resources & Customer Care.
  4. Localization of currency, date formats, business terminology, and
     example scenarios for the Vietnamese small-and-medium enterprise market.
  5. Minor configuration adjustments to .mcp.json (server identifier
     normalization, Square SSE transport correction).

